WEBVTT

00:00:06.694 --> 00:00:09.979
Prav zdaj verjetno sedite 
in gledate tale video.

00:00:09.979 --> 00:00:14.599
Nekajminutno sedenje je verjetno v redu.

00:00:14.599 --> 00:00:19.172
A dlje ko ste pri miru,
bolj nemirno postane telo.

00:00:19.172 --> 00:00:23.048
Šteje minute do trenutka,
ko boste spet vstali

00:00:23.048 --> 00:00:25.011
in šli na sprehod.

00:00:25.011 --> 00:00:26.711
Morda to zveni neumno.

00:00:26.711 --> 00:00:29.156
Naša telesa rada sedijo, ne?

00:00:29.156 --> 00:00:30.477
Niti ne.